WEBVTT

00:03:29.211 --> 00:03:31.850
would be about what happens
when high blood pressure

00:03:31.874 --> 00:03:33.500
is not adequately addressed.

00:03:35.318 --> 00:03:39.088
"Say, did you hear about Jimmy?
He had a stroke."

00:03:41.612 --> 00:03:45.867
"Did you hear about Eddie?
He died last week.

00:03:45.891 --> 00:03:47.579
Massive heart attack.

00:03:47.603 --> 00:03:48.795
He was 50."

00:03:50.584 --> 00:03:54.503
More black men die from high blood
pressure than from anything else,

00:03:54.527 --> 00:03:59.422
even though decades of medical wisdom
and science have demonstrated

00:03:59.446 --> 00:04:02.590
that death from high blood pressure
can be prevented